			<h1><u>About</u></h1>

			<h3>Who am I?</h3>
			<p class="info-text"> My new found journey into the tech world has fully solidified my "nerd" status. From code and design to gaming, to everywhere in between, I've always found myself engulfed. I spend most of my time now doing my best to join the two!</p>

			<h3>What do I do?</h3>
			<p class="info-text">I currently am working on open source projects and pet projects to further my craft. I am avidly searching for for a full time Jr. Developer position to put my roots down and really contribute my skills and learn from my team. I'm also always open to freelance/contract jobs for side work! </p>

